OL,6,FA Borders union leader has warned
OL,7,Fsocial care in the area is in a "dire"
OL,8,Fstate and staff are "exhausted."
OL,10,FIt comes as MSPs voted through a
OL,11,Frecord #21bn for health and social
OL,12,Fcare as part of the Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment's tax and spending plans
OL,14,Ffor the coming year.
OL,16,FA former carer in the region has told
OL,17,FITV Border the pressures of the job
OL,18,Fimpacted on her mental health and led
OL,19,Fto her decision to leave.
