OL,3,CBorders union leader has warned social
OL,4,Ccare in the area is in a 'dire' state
OL,6,FSpeaking anonymously, she said: "It
OL,7,Ftook a toll on my mental health, when
OL,8,FI complained nothing was done about
OL,9,Fit. There were times like half two in
OL,10,Fthe morning. I'm still wide awake
OL,11,Fbecause of all my stress. Everything
OL,12,Fwas just falling apart for me."
OL,14,FShe was employed by Scottish Borders
OL,15,FCouncil.
