OL,3,CBorders union leader has warned social
OL,4,Ccare in the area is in a 'dire' state
OL,6,FA spokesperson for their Adult Social
OL,7,FCare service said: "We take all
OL,8,Fconcerns regarding working conditions
OL,9,Fvery seriously and are committed to
OL,10,Fensuring the safety and well-being of
OL,11,Four staff.
OL,13,F"This includes adhering to strict safe
OL,14,Fstaffing guidelines to make sure our
OL,15,Fcarers can provide the highest quality
OL,16,Fof care to our clients. We utilise
OL,17,Fadvanced scheduling software that
OL,18,Faccurately calculates travel times,
OL,19,Fincluding walking routes, to ensure
OL,20,Fthat carers have sufficient time to
OL,21,Ftravel between clients.
