OL,6,F"This software helps to optimise
OL,7,Fschedules and reduces the need for
OL,8,Flengthy distances to be covered on
OL,9,Ffoot, especially during the evening
OL,10,Fshifts.
OL,12,F"Furthermore, we have established
OL,13,Fprotocols to address any staffing
OL,14,Fconcerns that are raised. Staff are
OL,15,Fencouraged to voice their concerns and
OL,16,Fprompt action is taken to address
OL,17,Fthese."
