OL,3,CBorders union leader has warned social
OL,4,Ccare in the area is in a 'dire' state
OL,6,FKaymarie Hughes, Scottish Borders
OL,7,FBranch Secretary, Unison, said: "It's
OL,8,Fabsolutely dire. We've had years of
OL,9,Funderfunding, it's really taken a toll.
OL,11,F"We've got staff leaving the job in
OL,12,Fdroves, both in health and social
OL,13,Fcare. There's so many members of staff
OL,14,Fthat are absolutely fed up, they're
OL,15,Ftired, they're exhausted, they feel
OL,16,Fundervalued and to be honest they can
OL,17,Fgo off somewhere else and work for the
OL,18,Fsame amount of money."
